/*
 Includes knots, linked rings, Moebius strips

 The three sliders (left->right) control the order, twist and connectivity;
 play with them to determine what does what (keep the middle value low to avoid artifacts).

 See: www.fractalforums.com/new-theories-and-research/not-fractal-but-funny-trefoil-knot-routine/
