// The Sarti Dodecic Surface, raymarched using the implicit equation as SDF,
// adjusted by the gradient, computed numerically either in the usual way,
// or with an imaginary delta, or using dual numbers.
//
// Good explanation from Nick Higham:
// https://nhigham.com/2020/10/06/what-is-the-complex-step-approximation/
//
// Fast it isn't, but the implicit function is quite complex.
//
// Matthew Arcus, mla, 2020.
//
// <mouse>: rotate
// <up>/<down>: move in/out
// <left>/<right>: fog distance or clip radius
// c: clip at clipradius sphere
// f: fog
// i: apply inversion
// l: light transform
// r: autorotation
// s: soft shadows
